title: Shoot for the Moon?
text:
Shoot for the Moon?

A basket ball hoop in the park, no-one is allowed to practice at the moment- don't understand why. It stands all alone, isolated between the football pitch and the cricket pitch, which are both also not in use.

nonsporty photographer - Jackie

Theme - Sport
